cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.SD, cs.LG

This paper deals with sentiment analysis of emojis in social media, which falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves data mining and machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with cross-lingual sentiment analysis, which could fall under cs.CY (Computational Linguistics and Natural Language Processing) and cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing).
